### keelemudeli genereeritud

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ─── Tables ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all tables
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tables
Accept: application/json

### Get all zones
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/zones
Accept: application/json

### Example zone response now includes openingTime/closingTime

### ─── Availability ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get table recommendations (minimal params)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/availability/recommendations
  ?startTime=2026-03-15T18:00:00
  &durationMinutes=90
  &partySize=2
  &zoneId=1
Accept: application/json

### Get recommendations outside zone opening hours (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/availability/recommendations
  ?startTime=2026-03-15T09:00:00
  &durationMinutes=60
  &partySize=2
  &zoneId=1
Accept: application/json

### Get table recommendations (window preferred)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/availability/recommendations
  ?startTime=2026-03-15T19:00:00
  &durationMinutes=60
  &partySize=4
  &zoneId=1
  &windowPreferred=true
  &privacyPreferred=false
Accept: application/json

### Get table recommendations (privacy preferred)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/availability/recommendations
  ?startTime=2026-03-16T20:00:00
  &durationMinutes=120
  &partySize=6
  &zoneId=2
  &windowPreferred=false
  &privacyPreferred=true
Accept: application/json

### ─── Bookings ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
  ?tableId=1
  &startTime=2026-03-15T18:00:00
  &durationMinutes=90
  &numberOfPeople=2
  &customerName=Jane%20Doe
  &customerPhone=%2B37255512345
Accept: application/json

### Create booking outside zone opening hours (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
  ?tableId=1
  &startTime=2026-03-15T22:30:00
  &durationMinutes=60
  &numberOfPeople=2
  &customerName=Late%20Guest
  &customerPhone=%2B37250000000
Accept: application/json

### Create a booking (larger group)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings
  ?tableId=3
  &startTime=2026-03-16T20:00:00
  &durationMinutes=120
  &numberOfPeople=5
  &customerName=John%20Smith
  &customerPhone=%2B37255598765
Accept: application/json

### Get bookings for a table on a specific day
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/by-table-and-day
  ?tableId=1
  &day=2026-03-15
Accept: application/json
